DSJobDef.name: P_TB_ODAPP_TB_MBMB_PRKADMTDC_L_01

Property.valueExpression:
SELECT PRK_ADMT_DC_DESC_NO                   AS PRK_ADMT_DC_DESC_NO  -- 주차정산할인내역번호
     , MBR_NO                                AS MBR_NO               -- 회원번호            
     , PRK_ADMT_DC_NO                        AS PRK_ADMT_DC_NO       -- 주차정산할인번호    
     , ORGIN_PRK_ADMT_DC_NO                  AS ORGIN_PRK_ADMT_DC_NO -- 원주차정산할인번호  
     , DC_TP_CD                              AS DC_TP_CD             -- 할인유형코드        
     , CSTR_CD                               AS CSTR_CD              -- 자점코드            
     , TRNS_DT                               AS TRNS_DT              -- 거래일자            
     , POS_NO                                AS POS_NO               -- 포스번호            
     , RCPT_NO                               AS RCPT_NO              -- 영수증번호          
     , SLNG_AMT                              AS SLNG_AMT             -- 매출금액            
     , CAR_NO                                AS CAR_NO               -- 차량번호            
     , CARETR_DT                             AS CARETR_DT            -- 입차일자            
     , CARETR_HMS                            AS CARETR_HMS           -- 입차시분초          
     , ORCPT_NO                              AS ORCPT_NO             -- 원영수증번호        
     , PRCS_RSLT_CD                          AS PRCS_RSLT_CD         -- 처리결과코드        
     , PRCS_RSLT_MSG_CONT                    AS PRCS_RSLT_CONT       -- 처리결과내용        
     , TO_CHAR(RGST_DTM, 'YYYYMMDDHH24MISS') AS RGST_DTM             -- 등록일시            
     , RGPR_ID                               AS RGPR_ID              -- 등록자아이디        
     , TO_CHAR(MDF_DTM, 'YYYYMMDDHH24MISS')  AS MDF_DTM              -- 수정일시            
     , MDFPR_ID                              AS MDFPR_ID             -- 수정자아이디        
     , TO_CHAR(SYSDATE, 'YYYYMMDDHH24MISS')  AS FNL_LOAD_DTM         -- 최종적재일시        
 FROM #P_DB_APP.$S_APP_SCM#.TB_MBMB_PRKADMTDC_L
WHERE RGST_DTM BETWEEN TO_DATE('#$S_FROM_YMD#' || '000000', 'YYYYMMDDHH24MISS')
                                     AND TO_DATE('#$S_TO_YMD#' || '235959', 'YYYYMMDDHH24MISS')
       OR MDF_DTM BETWEEN TO_DATE('#$S_FROM_YMD#' || '000000', 'YYYYMMDDHH24MISS')
                                     AND TO_DATE('#$S_TO_YMD#' || '235959', 'YYYYMMDDHH24MISS')
